skills.instructionTemplate:
Goal: produce or edit one local production_proposal draft for a single production. Do not create formal production entities.

Draft schema: {{schema:movscript.production_proposal.v1.id}}

{{schema:movscript.production_proposal.v1}}

Use context and draft tools: {{tool:movscript_get_current_context}} {{tool:movscript_create_draft}} {{tool:movscript_update_draft}}. Ask for projectId or productionId only when missing and necessary: {{tool:movscript_request_user_input}}.

Workflow: verify context, read any upstream project_proposal draft, find or create the production_proposal draft, patch with JSON Pointer operations, validate, then run preview_apply. If validation or backend errors appear, patch the specific paths and preview again.

Goal: maintain project_proposal first, then production_proposal from that upstream basis. Both artifacts remain local review drafts.

Project schema: {{schema:movscript.project_proposal.v1.id}}
{{schema:movscript.project_proposal.v1}}

Production schema: {{schema:movscript.production_proposal.v1.id}}
{{schema:movscript.production_proposal.v1}}

Use draft tools to find, create, patch, validate, and preview each draft. Preview the project draft before using its references in the production draft. If either preview fails, repair that draft before summarizing completion.

Goal: produce or edit a local asset_proposal draft for review before any generation job.

Draft schema: {{schema:movscript.asset_proposal.v1.id}}

{{schema:movscript.asset_proposal.v1}}

Plan concrete candidate prompts, references, model needs, risks, and acceptance criteria. Use draft tools only; do not create generation jobs in this workflow.

Goal: produce or edit a local content_unit_proposal draft for scene or content-unit structure.

Draft schema: {{schema:movscript.content_unit_proposal.v1.id}}

{{schema:movscript.content_unit_proposal.v1}}

Keep structure, media plans, and generated assets separate. Patch the draft, validate, and preview_apply before summarizing.

Goal: produce or edit a local content_unit_media_proposal draft for media, shots, or keyframes.

Draft schema: {{schema:movscript.content_unit_media_proposal.v1.id}}

{{schema:movscript.content_unit_media_proposal.v1}}

Reference existing content units and asset needs. Do not launch generation jobs here; keep this workflow as media planning and review.

Goal: create or edit a local script_split_proposal draft using source summaries and line ranges, not copied script body text.

Draft schema: {{schema:movscript.script_split_proposal.v1.id}}

{{schema:movscript.script_split_proposal.v1}}

Use context and draft tools to create, patch, validate, and preview_apply. Keep warnings for uncertain line ranges or missing source metadata.
